@baseUrl = http://localhost:9000
@rentableId = 7bebd3a2-3c01-44c0-a353-5e17e4ec92c4

### Check availability (no bookings)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/rentables/{{rentableId}}/availability?check_in=2026-06-01&check_out=2026-06-30

### Check availability — invalid date range (check_out before check_in)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/rentables/{{rentableId}}/availability?check_in=2026-07-10&check_out=2026-07-05

### Check availability — missing check_in
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/rentables/{{rentableId}}/availability?check_out=2026-07-04

### Check availability — rentable not found
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/rentables/rentable-tidak-ada/availability?check_in=2026-07-01&check_out=2026-07-04
